<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>高考数学 - 标签 - 凌乱之风的博客</title><link>https://messywind.github.io/tags/%E9%AB%98%E8%80%83%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6/</link><description>This is my new Hugo FixIt site</description><generator>Hugo 0.136.5 &amp; FixIt v0.3.13</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 00:54:49 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://messywind.github.io/tags/%E9%AB%98%E8%80%83%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>记一个经典不等式放缩</title><link>https://messywind.github.io/posts/%E8%AE%B0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E4%B8%8D%E7%AD%89%E5%BC%8F%E6%94%BE%E7%BC%A9/</link><pubDate>Wed, 06 Apr 2022 00:07:20 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://messywind.github.io/posts/%E8%AE%B0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BB%8F%E5%85%B8%E4%B8%8D%E7%AD%89%E5%BC%8F%E6%94%BE%E7%BC%A9/</guid><category domain="https://messywind.github.io/categories/%E6%9D%82%E9%A1%B9/">杂项</category><description>&lt;p>今晚闲来无事看了看 $2022$ 年的济南一模最后一题第三问，发现真的是两年没碰高考数学手生疏了，不过还好做出来了。
&lt;strong>题意&lt;/strong>
证明
$$
\sum_{x = 2}^{n} \frac{1}{\ln x} &amp;gt; 1 - \frac{1}{n}
$$
&lt;strong>分析：&lt;/strong>
$1 - \dfrac{1}{n} = \dfrac{n - 1}{n}$，左边是 $n$ 个数求和，所以考虑裂项右边&lt;/p>
&lt;p>$$
\frac{n - 1}{n} = \frac{1}{1 \times 2} + \frac{1}{2 \times 3} + \cdots + \frac{1}{(n - 1) \times n}
$$&lt;/p>
&lt;p>接下来只需证 $x ^ 2 - x - \ln x &amp;gt; 0 (x \ge 2)$&lt;/p>
&lt;p>设 $f(x) = x ^ 2 - x - \ln x$
则 $f&amp;rsquo;(x) = \dfrac{(2x+ 1)(x-1)}{x} &amp;gt; 0$
由于 $f(2) = 2 - \ln2 &amp;gt; 0$
所以 $f(x)&amp;gt; 0$&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>2021新高考全国Ⅰ卷 22题</title><link>https://messywind.github.io/posts/2021%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98%E8%80%83%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E5%8D%B7-22%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Tue, 08 Jun 2021 16:30:49 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://messywind.github.io/posts/2021%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98%E8%80%83%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E5%8D%B7-22%E9%A2%98/</guid><category domain="https://messywind.github.io/categories/%E6%9D%82%E9%A1%B9/">杂项</category><description>&lt;h2 id="题面" class="heading-element">&lt;span>题面:&lt;/span>
